
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "nctForum";
}

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport" />
    <title>
        HoYoLAB
    </title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com">
    </script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
           font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
         }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#1e2233] text-[#c1c1c1] min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex px-4 py-6 space-x-6 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
        <section class="flex-1 max-w-[720px]">
            <div class="bg-[#22263b] rounded-lg p-4">
                <nav class="flex space-x-6 border-b border-[#2a2e43] mb-4 text-sm font-semibold select-none">
                    <button class="text-[#a1a1a1] hover:text-white py-2">
                        Theo Dõi
                    </button>
                    <button class="text-white border-b-2 border-[#5f7fff] py-2 font-bold">
                        Đề Xuất
                    </button>
                    <button class="text-[#a1a1a1] hover:text-white py-2">
                        Sự Kiện
                    </button>
                </nav>
                <article class="text-xs text-[#a1a1a1]">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-1">
                        <img alt="User avatar with white hair and purple background" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full" height="32" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/00a0ad6e-d2e8-47c3-cb22-8b57a406abaf.jpg" width="32" />
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 font-semibold text-white select-text">
                            <span>
                                Your Fab
                            </span>
                            <i class="fas fa-robot text-xs">
                            </i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="ml-2 text-[10px] text-[#6b6b6b] select-text">
                            2 ngày trước · Genshin Impact
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white font-bold mb-1 leading-tight">
                        5.6 Mới ( 01-05-2025 ) 7 Mã Mới Đến đây
                        <span>
                            🔥
                        </span>
                        - Tổng ×410 Nguyên Thạch
                        <span>
                            🔥
                        </span>
                        (Kiểm tra Nở rộ từ trong bóng tối
                        <span class="inline-block bg-[#2f7f3f] rounded px-1 select-text">
                            ✅
                        </span>
                        )
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-3 leading-tight">
                        <span class="inline-block select-text">
                            ≡ Đến đây Là Mới ×60 Nguyên Thạch Mã ( Hôm nay ) ( MÃ 1 ) - ZT5RJ4AX4WYV ( SAO CHÉP MÃ NÀY VÀ NHẤP VÀO ĐÂY ĐỂ NHẬN - &gt;&gt; Lạch cạch Đến đây Để Nhận &lt;&lt; ≡Nội Dung Thưởng ×60 Nguyên Thạch &amp; Kho Sách ( Tất Cả Mã )
                        </span>
                    </p>
                    <img alt="Claim rewards image showing three crystals with values 60, 200, 150 and a red arrow pointing to a claim button dated 01-05-2025" class="rounded-lg mb-3" height="250" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/a67867f8-d9ad-4bad-c328-c42735f3e784.jpg" width="600" />
                    <div class="flex space-x-2 text-[#5f7fff] text-xs select-text mb-2">
                        <span>
                            <i class="fas fa-fire">
                            </i>
                            Raiden Shogun
                        </span>
                        <span>
                            # Mã Đổi
                        </span>
                        <span>
                            # Mayuika
                        </span>
                        <span>
                            # Arlecchino
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-[#6b6b6b] text-xs select-none">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                            <i class="far fa-eye">
                            </i>
                            <span>
                                253K
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                            <i class="far fa-comment">
                            </i>
                            <span>
                                217
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                            <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up">
                            </i>
                            <span>
                                2557
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
        <aside class="w-72 space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-[#22263b] rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 select-none">
                    Mau đến gửi bài nào
                </h3>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 text-xs text-white select-none">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#2f7f3f] flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-pen text-white text-lg">
                            </i>
                        </div>
                        <span>
                            Bài Viết
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 text-xs text-white select-none">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#3f7f9f] flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-image text-white text-lg">
                            </i>
                        </div>
                        <span>
                            Hình Ảnh
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 text-xs text-white select-none">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#7f6f2f] flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-video text-white text-lg">
                            </i>
                        </div>
                        <span>
                            Video
                        </span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#22263b] rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 select-none flex items-center justify-between">
                    Genshin Impact
                    <i class="fas fa-caret-down text-xs">
                    </i>
                </h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-xs text-[#a1a1a1] select-none">
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a treasure chest for Hộp Công Cụ" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/37932775-fcbc-4059-f4e1-d7c37e30b61f.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Hộp Công Cụ
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a star for Điểm Danh" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/4f204dad-e4af-4871-c372-0976141e27fd.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Điểm Danh
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a moon for Bài Ca Không Nguyệt" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/ee2ff1b5-cb4e-4937-a90a-554827ae192f.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Bài Ca Không Nguyệt
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of an egg for Bồi Dưỡng Saurian Nhận.." class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/0f285b29-8e11-44fc-01f1-0d287365af97.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Bồi Dưỡng Saurian Nhận..
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a box for Tiện Ích" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/4f19f2e5-45c5-494f-7dfb-dc91d44bf952.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Tiện Ích
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a book for HoYoWiki" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/c75452b5-433f-4ffa-9947-18f1b24a43a5.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            HoYoWiki
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a map for Bản Đồ Tương Tác Teyvat" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/25337060-09e6-458a-5b35-dce564f5facc.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Bản Đồ Tương Tác Teyvat
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a medal for Chiến tích" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/89f367a4-49bc-46a2-f62d-5b5d9e3b27df.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            Chiến tích
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1">
                        <img alt="Icon of a sketch for HoYoSketch" class="w-10 h-10" height="40" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/96f010cd-d20c-406b-5d4c-d1c3216d8bd3.jpg" width="40" />
                        <span>
                            HoYoSketch
                        </span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </main>
</body>
</html>


